== Deaths == * {{ill|Empress Suiko|ja|жҺЁеҸӨеӨ©зҡҮ|12=draft|12=draft}} 34th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft}} [[626]] {{ill|June 19|ja|6жңҲ19ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Soga no Umako|ja|иҳҮжҲ‘йҰ¬еӯҗ|12=draft|12=draft}}, a courtier and father of {{ill|Soga no Ezo|ja|иҳҮжҲ‘Ezo|12=draft|12=draft}} (born circa [[551]])<ref name="seinengappi">{{Cite book | title=жү¶жЎ‘з•ҘиЁҳ | publisher= | year= | page= | note=Calculated from an age of 76; some sources associate his name вҖңUmakoвҖқ with a birth year in the [[GengЕҚ]] of Emperor Kinmei }}</ref>. * {{ill|Tenpuku (Japan)|ja|еӨ©зҰҸ|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1234]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6жңҲ18ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|ChukЕҚ TennЕҚ|ja|д»ІжҒӯеӨ©зҡҮ|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 85th Emperor of Japan (born circa [[1218]]). * {{ill|Meio|ja|жҳҺеҝң|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1496]] {{ill|June 30|ja|6жңҲ30ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Hino Tomiko|ja|ж—ҘйҮҺеҜҢеӯҗ|12=draft|12=draft}}, wife of {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshimasa|ja|и¶іеҲ©зҫ©ж”ҝ|12=draft|12=draft}} (born circa [[1440]]). * {{ill|KeichЕҚ|ja|ж…¶й•·|12=draft|12=draft}} 19th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|гӮ°гғ¬гӮҙгғӘгӮӘжҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1614]] {{ill|June 27|ja|6жңҲ27ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Maeda Tosanaga|ja|еүҚз”°еҲ©й•·|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 2nd lord of the {{ill|Kaga Domain|ja|еҠ иіҖи—©|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[1562]]).
