== Events == * {{ill|Wutoku|ja|жӯҰеҫі|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft}} [[618]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6жңҲ18ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Li Yuan|ja|жқҺж·ө|12=draft|12=draft}} received abdication from {{ill|Sui Emperor Gongdi You|ja|жҒӯеёқдҫ‘|12=draft|12=draft}} of the Sui dynasty and ascended the throne (as Emperor Gaozu), marking the establishment of the {{ill|Tang|ja|е”җ|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|ChЕҚhЕҚ|ja|й•·дҝқ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft}} [[999]] {{ill|July 5|ja|7жңҲ5ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ An imperial edict posthumously awarded {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|иҸ…еҺҹйҒ“зңҹ|12=draft|12=draft}} the offices of {{ill|Sadaijin|ja|е·ҰеӨ§иҮЈ|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|ShЕҚichii|ja|жӯЈдёҖдҪҚ|12=draft|12=draft}}, and established the {{ill|Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|ja|еҢ—йҮҺзҘһзӨҫ|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|ЕҢnin|ja|еҝңд»Ғ|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1467]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6жңҲ21ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ During the {{ill|ЕҢnin War|ja|еҝңд»ҒгҒ®д№ұ|12=draft|12=draft}}, commanders such as {{ill|Yamana Mochitoyo|ja|еұұеҗҚжҢҒиұҠ|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Hatakeyama Yoshinobu|ja|з• еұұзҫ©е°ұ|12=draft|12=draft}} raised armies.
