== Events == * {{ill|Wutoku|ja|жӯҰеҫі|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[618]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6жңҲ18ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Li Yuan|ja|жқҺж·ө|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} received abdication from {{ill|Sui Emperor Gongdi You|ja|жҒӯеёқдҫ‘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of the Sui dynasty and ascended the throne (as Emperor Gaozu), marking the establishment of the {{ill|Tang|ja|е”җ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|ChЕҚhЕҚ|ja|й•·дҝқ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[999]] {{ill|July 5|ja|7жңҲ5ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ An imperial edict posthumously awarded {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|иҸ…еҺҹйҒ“зңҹ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the offices of {{ill|Sadaijin|ja|е·ҰеӨ§иҮЈ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|ShЕҚichii|ja|жӯЈдёҖдҪҚ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and established the {{ill|Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|ja|еҢ—йҮҺзҘһзӨҫ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|ЕҢnin|ja|еҝңд»Ғ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1467]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6жңҲ21ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ During the {{ill|ЕҢnin War|ja|еҝңд»ҒгҒ®д№ұ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, commanders such as {{ill|Yamana Mochitoyo|ja|еұұеҗҚжҢҒиұҠ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Hatakeyama Yoshinobu|ja|з• еұұзҫ©е°ұ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} raised armies.
== Births ==
== Deaths == * {{ill|Empress Suiko|ja|жҺЁеҸӨеӨ©зҡҮ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 34th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[626]] {{ill|June 19|ja|6жңҲ19ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Soga no Umako|ja|иҳҮжҲ‘йҰ¬еӯҗ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a courtier and father of {{ill|Soga no Ezo|ja|иҳҮжҲ‘Ezo|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born circa [[551]])<ref name="seinengappi">{{Cite book | title=жү¶жЎ‘з•ҘиЁҳ | publisher= | year= | page= | note=Calculated from an age of 76; some sources associate his name вҖңUmakoвҖқ with a birth year in the [[GengЕҚ]] of Emperor Kinmei }}</ref>. * {{ill|Tenpuku (Japan)|ja|еӨ©зҰҸ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1234]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6жңҲ18ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|ChukЕҚ TennЕҚ|ja|д»ІжҒӯеӨ©зҡҮ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 85th Emperor of Japan (born circa [[1218]]). * {{ill|Meio|ja|жҳҺеҝң|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1496]] {{ill|June 30|ja|6жңҲ30ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Hino Tomiko|ja|ж—ҘйҮҺеҜҢеӯҗ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, wife of {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshimasa|ja|и¶іеҲ©зҫ©ж”ҝ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born circa [[1440]]). * {{ill|KeichЕҚ|ja|ж…¶й•·|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 19th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|гӮ°гғ¬гӮҙгғӘгӮӘжҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1614]] {{ill|June 27|ja|6жңҲ27ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Maeda Tosanaga|ja|еүҚз”°еҲ©й•·|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 2nd lord of the {{ill|Kaga Domain|ja|еҠ иіҖи—©|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[1562]]).
