•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1467]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6жңҲ21ж—Ҙ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) вҖ“ During the {{ill|ЕҢnin War|ja|еҝңд»ҒгҒ®д№ұ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, commanders such as {{ill|Yamana Mochitoyo|ja|еұұеҗҚжҢҒиұҠ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Hatakeyama Yoshinobu|ja|з• еұұзҫ©е°ұ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} raised armies.
