'''May 20''' is the 20th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5жңҲ (ж—§жҡҰ)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|ж—§жҡҰ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|RokuyЕҚ|ja|е…ӯжӣң|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|ShakkЕҚ|ja|иөӨеҸЈ|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Wutoku|ja|жӯҰеҫі|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[618]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6жңҲ18ж—Ҙ|qq=|12=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Li Yuan|ja|жқҺж·ө|qq=|12=draft}} received abdication from {{ill|Sui Emperor Gongdi You|ja|жҒӯеёқдҫ‘|qq=|12=draft}} of the Sui dynasty and ascended the throne (as Emperor Gaozu), marking the establishment of the {{ill|Tang|ja|е”җ|qq=|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|ChЕҚhЕҚ|ja|й•·дҝқ|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[999]] {{ill|July 5|ja|7жңҲ5ж—Ҙ|qq=|12=draft}}) вҖ“ An imperial edict posthumously awarded {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|иҸ…еҺҹйҒ“зңҹ|qq=|12=draft}} the offices of {{ill|Sadaijin|ja|е·ҰеӨ§иҮЈ|qq=|12=draft}} and {{ill|ShЕҚichii|ja|жӯЈдёҖдҪҚ|qq=|12=draft}}, and established the {{ill|Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|ja|еҢ—йҮҺзҘһзӨҫ|qq=|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|ЕҢnin|ja|еҝңд»Ғ|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1467]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6жңҲ21ж—Ҙ|qq=|12=draft}}) вҖ“ During the {{ill|ЕҢnin War|ja|еҝңд»ҒгҒ®д№ұ|qq=|12=draft}}, commanders such as {{ill|Yamana Mochitoyo|ja|еұұеҗҚжҢҒиұҠ|qq=|12=draft}} and {{ill|Hatakeyama Yoshinobu|ja|з• еұұзҫ©е°ұ|qq=|12=draft}} raised armies.

