{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=дә”жңҲдәҢеҚҒ|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=мқҢл Ҙ 5мӣ” 20мқј|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 20''' is the 20th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5жңҲ (ж—§жҡҰ)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|ж—§жҡҰ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft}}. Its {{ill|RokuyЕҚ|ja|е…ӯжӣң|qq=|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|ShakkЕҚ|ja|иөӨеҸЈ|qq=|qq=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Wutoku|ja|жӯҰеҫі|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[618]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6жңҲ18ж—Ҙ|qq=|qq=draft}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Li Yuan|ja|жқҺж·ө|qq=|qq=draft}} received abdication from {{ill|Sui Emperor Gongdi You|ja|жҒӯеёқдҫ‘|qq=|qq=draft}} of the Sui dynasty and ascended the throne (as Emperor Gaozu), marking the establishment of the {{ill|Tang|ja|е”җ|qq=|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|ChЕҚhЕҚ|ja|й•·дҝқ|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[999]] {{ill|July 5|ja|7жңҲ5ж—Ҙ|qq=|qq=draft}}) вҖ“ An imperial edict posthumously awarded {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|иҸ…еҺҹйҒ“зңҹ|qq=|qq=draft}} the offices of {{ill|Sadaijin|ja|е·ҰеӨ§иҮЈ|qq=|qq=draft}} and {{ill|ShЕҚichii|ja|жӯЈдёҖдҪҚ|qq=|qq=draft}}, and established the {{ill|Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|ja|еҢ—йҮҺзҘһзӨҫ|qq=|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|ЕҢnin|ja|еҝңд»Ғ|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1467]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6жңҲ21ж—Ҙ|qq=|qq=draft}}) вҖ“ During the {{ill|ЕҢnin War|ja|еҝңд»ҒгҒ®д№ұ|qq=|qq=draft}}, commanders such as {{ill|Yamana Mochitoyo|ja|еұұеҗҚжҢҒиұҠ|qq=|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Hatakeyama Yoshinobu|ja|з• еұұзҫ©е°ұ|qq=|qq=draft}} raised armies.
