== Events == * {{ill|Wutoku|ja|жӯҰеҫі|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wutoku|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[618]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6жңҲ18ж—Ҙ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 18|qq=}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Li Yuan|ja|жқҺж·ө|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Li Yuan|qq=}} received abdication from {{ill|Sui Emperor Gongdi You|ja|жҒӯеёқдҫ‘|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sui Emperor Gongdi You|qq=}} of the Sui dynasty and ascended the throne (as Emperor Gaozu), marking the establishment of the {{ill|Tang|ja|е”җ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tang|qq=}}. * {{ill|ChЕҚhЕҚ|ja|й•·дҝқ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ChЕҚhЕҚ|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[999]] {{ill|July 5|ja|7жңҲ5ж—Ҙ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 5|qq=}}) вҖ“ An imperial edict posthumously awarded {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|иҸ…еҺҹйҒ“зңҹ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sugawara no Michizane|qq=}} the offices of {{ill|Sadaijin|ja|е·ҰеӨ§иҮЈ|1=Minister of the Left|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sadaijin|qq=}} and {{ill|ShЕҚichii|ja|жӯЈдёҖдҪҚ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ShЕҚichii|qq=}}, and established the {{ill|Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|ja|еҢ—йҮҺзҘһзӨҫ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|qq=}}. * {{ill|ЕҢnin|ja|еҝңд»Ғ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ЕҢnin|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1467]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6жңҲ21ж—Ҙ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 21|qq=}}) вҖ“ During the {{ill|ЕҢnin War|ja|еҝңд»ҒгҒ®д№ұ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ЕҢnin War|qq=}}, commanders such as {{ill|Yamana Mochitoyo|ja|еұұеҗҚжҢҒиұҠ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamana Mochitoyo|qq=}} and {{ill|Hatakeyama Yoshinobu|ja|з• еұұзҫ©е°ұ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hatakeyama Yoshinobu|qq=}} raised armies.
