{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=дә”жңҲдәҢеҚҒ|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=мқҢл Ҙ 5мӣ” 20мқј|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 20''' is the 20th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5жңҲ (ж—§жҡҰ)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|ж—§жҡҰ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|RokuyЕҚ|ja|е…ӯжӣң|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/RokuyЕҚ|qq=}} day is {{ill|ShakkЕҚ|ja|иөӨеҸЈ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ShakkЕҚ|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Wutoku|ja|жӯҰеҫі|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wutoku|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[618]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6жңҲ18ж—Ҙ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 18|qq=}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Li Yuan|ja|жқҺж·ө|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Li Yuan|qq=}} received abdication from {{ill|Sui Emperor Gongdi You|ja|жҒӯеёқдҫ‘|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sui Emperor Gongdi You|qq=}} of the Sui dynasty and ascended the throne (as Emperor Gaozu), marking the establishment of the {{ill|Tang|ja|е”җ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tang|qq=}}. * {{ill|ChЕҚhЕҚ|ja|й•·дҝқ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ChЕҚhЕҚ|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[999]] {{ill|July 5|ja|7жңҲ5ж—Ҙ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 5|qq=}}) вҖ“ An imperial edict posthumously awarded {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|иҸ…еҺҹйҒ“зңҹ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sugawara no Michizane|qq=}} the offices of {{ill|Sadaijin|ja|е·ҰеӨ§иҮЈ|1=Minister of the Left|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sadaijin|qq=}} and {{ill|Senior First Rank|lt=Senior First Rank|lt=ShЕҚichii|ja|жӯЈдёҖдҪҚ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ShЕҚichii|qq=}}, and established the {{ill|Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|ja|еҢ—йҮҺзҘһзӨҫ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|qq=}}. * {{ill|ЕҢnin|ja|еҝңд»Ғ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ЕҢnin|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=гғҰгғӘгӮҰгӮ№жҡҰ|4=zh|5=е„’з•ҘжӣҶ|6=ru|7=Р®Р»РёР°РҪСҒРәРёР№_РәР°Р»РөРҪРҙР°СҖСҢ|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1467]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6жңҲ21ж—Ҙ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 21|qq=}}) вҖ“ During the {{ill|ЕҢnin War|ja|еҝңд»ҒгҒ®д№ұ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ЕҢnin War|qq=}}, commanders such as {{ill|Yamana Mochitoyo|ja|еұұеҗҚжҢҒиұҠ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamana Mochitoyo|qq=}} and {{ill|Hatakeyama Yoshinobu|ja|з• еұұзҫ©е°ұ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hatakeyama Yoshinobu|qq=}} raised armies.
