== Events == * {{ill|Wutoku|ja|жӯҰеҫі|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wutoku|qq=|1=Wude|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1041688}} 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:618|618]] [[:en:June 18|June 18]]) вҖ“ [[:en:Emperor Gaozu of Tang|Li Yuan]] received abdication from [[:en:Yang You|Sui Emperor Gongdi You]] of the Sui dynasty and ascended the throne (as Emperor Gaozu), marking the establishment of the [[:en:Tang dynasty|Tang]]. * [[:en:ChЕҚhЕҚ (era)|ChЕҚhЕҚ]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:999|999]] [[:en:July 5|July 5]]) вҖ“ An imperial edict posthumously awarded [[:en:Sugawara no Michizane|Sugawara no Michizane]] the offices of [[:en:Minister of the Left|Minister of the Left]] and {{ill|Senior First Rank|lt=Senior First Rank|lt=ShЕҚichii|ja|жӯЈдёҖдҪҚ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ShЕҚichii|qq=}}, and established the {{ill|Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|ja|еҢ—йҮҺзҘһзӨҫ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to еҢ—йҮҺеӨ©жәҖе®®|1=Kitano TenmangЕ«|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q662176}}. * [[:en:ЕҢnin|ЕҢnin]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1467|1467]] [[:en:June 21|June 21]]) вҖ“ During the [[:en:ЕҢnin War|ЕҢnin War]], commanders such as {{ill|Yamana Mochitoyo|ja|еұұеҗҚжҢҒиұҠ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamana Mochitoyo|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to еұұеҗҚе®—е…Ё|1=Yamana SЕҚzen|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1355689}} and [[:en:Hatakeyama Yoshinari|Hatakeyama Yoshinobu]] raised armies.
== Births ==
== Deaths == * [[:en:Empress Suiko|Empress Suiko]] 34th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:626|626]] [[:en:June 19|June 19]]) вҖ“ [[:en:Soga no Umako|Soga no Umako]], a courtier and father of {{ill|Soga no Ezo|ja|иҳҮжҲ‘Ezo|1=Soga no Emishi|2=ja|3=иҳҮжҲ‘иқҰеӨ·|qid=Q1292368|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga no Ezo|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} (born circa [[:en:551|551]])<ref name="seinengappi">{{Cite book | title=жү¶жЎ‘з•ҘиЁҳ | publisher= | year= | page= | note=Calculated from an age of 76; some sources associate his name вҖңUmakoвҖқ with a birth year in the [[GengЕҚ]] of Emperor Kinmei |qq=}}</ref>. * {{ill|Tenpuku (Japan)|ja|еӨ©зҰҸ|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpuku (Japan)|qq=|1=Tenpuku (Japan)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1305722}} 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1234|1234]] [[:en:June 18|June 18]]) вҖ“ [[:en:Emperor ChЕ«kyЕҚ|ChukЕҚ TennЕҚ]], the 85th Emperor of Japan (born circa [[:en:1218|1218]]). * [[:en:MeiЕҚ|Meio]] 5th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1496|1496]] [[:en:June 30|June 30]]) вҖ“ [[:en:Hino Tomiko|Hino Tomiko]], wife of [[:en:Ashikaga Yoshimasa|Ashikaga Yoshimasa]] (born circa [[:en:1440|1440]]). * [[:en:KeichЕҚ|KeichЕҚ]] 19th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1614|1614]] [[:en:June 27|June 27]]) вҖ“ [[:en:Maeda Toshinaga|Maeda Tosanaga]], the 2nd lord of the [[:en:Kaga Domain|Kaga Domain]] (born [[:en:1562|1562]]).
