'''May 20''' is the 20th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5жңҲ (ж—§жҡҰ)|lt=May (Satsuki)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|ж—§жҡҰ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|RokuyЕҚ|ja|е…ӯжӣң|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/RokuyЕҚ|qq=}} day is {{ill|ShakkЕҚ|ja|иөӨеҸЈ|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ShakkЕҚ|1=ShakkЕҚ|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11635368}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Wutoku|ja|жӯҰеҫі|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wutoku|1=Wude|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1041688}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|618|en|618|qid=Q31035|lt=618|1=618}} {{ill|June 18|en|June 18|qid=Q2670|lt=June 18|1=June 18}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Emperor Gaozu of Tang|en|Emperor Gaozu of Tang|qid=Q9700|lt=Li Yuan|1=Emperor Gaozu of Tang}} received abdication from {{ill|Yang You|en|Yang You|qid=Q7420|lt=Sui Emperor Gongdi You|1=Yang You}} of the Sui dynasty and ascended the throne (as Emperor Gaozu), marking the establishment of the {{ill|Tang dynasty|en|Tang dynasty|qid=Q9683|lt=Tang|1=Tang dynasty}}.
* {{ill|ChЕҚhЕҚ (era)|en|ChЕҚhЕҚ (era)|qid=Q1324844|lt=ChЕҚhЕҚ|1=ChЕҚhЕҚ (era)}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|999|en|999|qid=Q277307|lt=999|1=999}} {{ill|July 5|en|July 5|qid=Q2696|lt=July 5|1=July 5}}) вҖ“ An imperial edict posthumously awarded {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|en|Sugawara no Michizane|qid=Q382005|lt=Sugawara no Michizane|1=Sugawara no Michizane}} the offices of {{ill|Minister of the Left|en|Minister of the Left|qid=Q949008|lt=Minister of the Left|1=Minister of the Left}} and {{ill|Senior First Rank|lt=Senior First Rank|lt=ShЕҚichii|ja|жӯЈдёҖдҪҚ|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/ShЕҚichii|qq=}}, and established the {{ill|Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|ja|еҢ—йҮҺзҘһзӨҫ|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kitano Tenmangu Shrine|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to еҢ—йҮҺеӨ©жәҖе®®|1=Kitano TenmangЕ«|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q662176}}.
* {{ill|ЕҢnin|en|ЕҢnin|qid=Q1143903|lt=ЕҢnin|1=ЕҢnin}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1467|en|1467|qid=Q6561|lt=1467|1=1467}} {{ill|June 21|en|June 21|qid=Q2671|lt=June 21|1=June 21}}) вҖ“ During the {{ill|ЕҢnin War|en|ЕҢnin War|qid=Q385676|lt=ЕҢnin War|1=ЕҢnin War}}, commanders such as {{ill|Yamana Mochitoyo|ja|еұұеҗҚжҢҒиұҠ|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamana Mochitoyo|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to еұұеҗҚе®—е…Ё|1=Yamana SЕҚzen|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1355689}} and {{ill|Hatakeyama Yoshinari|en|Hatakeyama Yoshinari|qid=Q11578676|lt=Hatakeyama Yoshinobu|1=Hatakeyama Yoshinari}} raised armies.

