* {{ill|Empress Suiko|en|Empress Suiko|qid=Q298057|lt=Empress Suiko|1=Empress Suiko}} 34th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|626|en|626|qid=Q31052|lt=626|1=626}} {{ill|June 19|en|June 19|qid=Q2669|lt=June 19|1=June 19}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Soga no Umako|en|Soga no Umako|qid=Q1191233|lt=Soga no Umako|1=Soga no Umako}}, a courtier and father of {{ill|Soga no Ezo|ja|иҳҮжҲ‘Ezo|1=Soga no Emishi|2=ja|3=иҳҮжҲ‘иқҰеӨ·|qid=Q1292368|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga no Ezo|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1292368}} (born circa {{ill|551|en|551|qid=Q30943|lt=551|1=551}})<ref name="seinengappi">{{Cite book | title=жү¶жЎ‘з•ҘиЁҳ | publisher= | year= | page= | note=Calculated from an age of 76; some sources associate his name вҖңUmakoвҖқ with a birth year in the [[GengЕҚ]] of Emperor Kinmei |qq=}}</ref>.
* {{ill|Tenpuku (Japan)|ja|еӨ©зҰҸ|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpuku (Japan)|1=Q1305722|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q1305722}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1234|en|1234|qid=Q5424|lt=1234|1=1234}} {{ill|June 18|en|June 18|qid=Q2670|lt=June 18|1=June 18}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Emperor ChЕ«kyЕҚ|en|Emperor ChЕ«kyЕҚ|qid=Q357253|lt=ChukЕҚ TennЕҚ|1=Emperor ChЕ«kyЕҚ}}, the 85th Emperor of Japan (born circa {{ill|1218|en|1218|qid=Q5381|lt=1218|1=1218}}).
* {{ill|MeiЕҚ|en|MeiЕҚ|qid=Q1193841|lt=Meio|1=MeiЕҚ}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1496|en|1496|qid=Q6699|lt=1496|1=1496}} {{ill|June 30|en|June 30|qid=Q2657|lt=June 30|1=June 30}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Hino Tomiko|en|Hino Tomiko|qid=Q5306708|lt=Hino Tomiko|1=Hino Tomiko}}, wife of {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshimasa|en|Ashikaga Yoshimasa|qid=Q447034|lt=Ashikaga Yoshimasa|1=Ashikaga Yoshimasa}} (born circa {{ill|1440|en|1440|qid=Q6384|lt=1440|1=1440}}).
* {{ill|KeichЕҚ|en|KeichЕҚ|qid=Q1328185|lt=KeichЕҚ|1=KeichЕҚ}} 19th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1614|en|1614|qid=Q6781|lt=1614|1=1614}} {{ill|June 27|en|June 27|qid=Q2664|lt=June 27|1=June 27}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Maeda Toshinaga|en|Maeda Toshinaga|qid=Q1186742|lt=Maeda Tosanaga|1=Maeda Toshinaga}}, the 2nd lord of the {{ill|Kaga Domain|en|Kaga Domain|qid=Q903448|lt=Kaga Domain|1=Kaga Domain}} (born {{ill|1562|en|1562|qid=Q6621|lt=1562|1=1562}}).

